    <h1>Privacy Policy for Cleanify</h1>
    <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> December 2024</p>
    
    <h2>Information We Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Device identifiers for advertising purposes (through Google AdMob)</li>
        <li>App usage analytics (crashes, performance data)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Information We DON'T Collect</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>Personal files or media content</li>
        <li>Contact information or personal data</li>
        <li>Location data</li>
        <li>Photos or videos (we only scan file metadata)</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>How We Use Information</h2>
    <ul>
        <li>To display relevant advertisements through Google AdMob</li>
        <li>To improve app performance and fix bugs</li>
    </ul>
    
    <h2>Third Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use Google AdMob which may collect device identifiers for advertising purposes. Please see Google's privacy policy for more information.</p>
    
    <h2>Data Security</h2>
    <p>Cleanify only accesses media files you choose to scan. We do not upload, store, or transmit your personal files.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at: [shig.jm@gmail.com]</p>
    
    <p><em>This policy may be updated from time to time. Please check back periodically for changes.</em></p>
